(II) $P\{X \leq Y\} = 1$.



{
    "步骤一": "求 $Y$ 的分布函数 $F(y)$:\n\[F(y) = P\{Y \leq y\} = P\{Y \leq y, X \leq 1\} + P\{Y \leq y, 1 < X < 2\} + P\{Y \leq y, X \geq 2\}\]\n\[= P\{2 \leq y, X \leq 1\} + P\{X \leq y, 1 < X < 2\} + P\{1 \leq y, X \geq 2\}\]\n当 $y < 1$ 时，$F(y) = 0$,\n当 $1 \leq y < 2$ 时：\n\[F(y) = P\{X \leq y, 1 < X < 2\} + P\{X \geq 2\} = P\{1 < X \leq y\} + P\{X \geq 2\}\]\n\[= \int_{1}^{y} \frac{1}{9}x^2 dx + \int_{2}^{3} \frac{1}{9}x^2 dx = \frac{1}{27}(y^3 - 1) + \frac{1}{27}(27 - 8) = \frac{1}{27}(y^3 + 18)\]\n当 $y \geq 2$ 时，$F(y) = 1$.",
    "步骤二": "求概率 $P\{X \leq Y\}$。\n根据给定的 $Y$ 的条件，$P\{X \leq Y\}$ 即为所有条件下的交集概率。\n通过完成对两个不相交的条件区域的积分求得。\n最终得到 $P\{X \leq Y\} = 1$。"
